Written by the fail2zig contributors.
.
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/ul0gic/fail2zig/issues
.UE .
.PP
Known limitations in v0.1.0:
.IP \(bu 2
The
.B reload
command is a stub; restart the daemon to apply config changes.
.IP \(bu 2
The
.B \-\-duration
flag on the
.B ban
command is accepted but the daemon currently uses the jail's configured
.B bantime
in all cases. This will be honored in v0.2.0.
.
.SH HISTORY
fail2zig-client 0.1.0 was the first public release, April 2026.
